PNMC INSTALLATION

# Requirements

  * C++14 compiler
    - clang >= 3.4
    - gcc >= 4.9.2
    - Other compilers might work, as long as they implement the C++14 standard

  * Libraries
    - libsdd (https://github.com/ahamez/libsdd)
    - Boost >= 1.58 (http://www.boost.org)

  * Tools
    - cmake >= 2.8.9

# Compilation

  * Quick start
    $ mkdir build
    $ cmake /path/to/pnmc -DLIBSDD_PATH=/path/to/libsdd
    $ make
    $ make install

  * CMake variables to configure paths
    - CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/install
    - BOOST_ROOT=/path/to/boost
    - CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/path/to/bin/compiler
